    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick &amp; Addictive Gameplay</strong><br>Aye Leon is a bite-sized blast of fun! With a full play through clocking in at around 20 minutes, it's perfect for quick breaks or replayable marathons. Easy to pick up, tough to put down.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 Unlockable Achievements</strong> <br>Turn a 20-minute run into a full-on challenge! Test your reflexes, find every hidden gem, and snag all 7 achievements. Quick game, lasting bragging rights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original Soundtrack by Jetset2one6</strong><br>Immerse yourself in a unique audio experience with exclusive tracks crafted by music producer Jetset2one6.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two Distinct Game Modes</strong><br>Choose your challenge:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lives Mode</strong>: How long can you last with limited lives?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Timed Mode</strong>: Race against the clock. Can you finish the game before time runs out?</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gravity called. Leon declined.... GO LEON!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197610/extras/ad56f4622c6cf5c836c1ddee835b8ccd.poster.avif?t=1767718505\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197610/extras/ad56f4622c6cf5c836c1ddee835b8ccd.webm?t=1767718505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197610/extras/ad56f4622c6cf5c836c1ddee835b8ccd.mp4?t=1767718505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
